<br>
I have been told the real secret to taking him down is 55+ wizards. Another person said pets that have naturally high MR/CR to start with, and to have casters chain cast pets.<br>
<br>
The plan that I have so far is two fold. One, 7 full groups, 3 tank and 4 caster. Two, to make sure every person on the raid is symboled and rune'd for max hps. (I am paying for all expenses and stones up front)<br>
<br>
I am open to any other suggestions before I attempt this huge endevour.<br>
<br>
Any strategies anyone wants to pass my way I am all ears for.<br>
<br>
I would expect anyone that came to raid would have some kind of CR gear by the time they are post 50 to start with, or I would hope so anyways, hehehe.<br>
<br>
*ready to listen intently*<br>
*hugs*<br>
<br>
