<br>
First, Gore casts a cold based AE slow/damage spell. It's resistable with enough CR, but even a 60 tank wont resist it every time and she does it a lot, so don't count on your tanks to finish her. <br>
<br>
Her other notable skill is her complete heal. Since tanks will NOT be fast enough to interrupt it with the slow on in all likelihood you'll have to rely on bards or chanters to sieve/occlude her butt. <br>
<br>
